Namespace Argotic.Publishing

Classes

AtomAcceptedMediaRange

Represents a media range as defined in RFC 2616: Hypertext Transfer Protocol that specifies a type of representation that can be added to a AtomMemberResources.

AtomCategoryDocument

Represents a list of categories available to be used when categorizing web resources.

AtomEntryResource

Represents a resource whose IRI is listed in a AtomFeed and uses AtomEntry as its representation.

AtomMemberResources

Describes the location and capabilities of a discoverable resource that contains a set of member resources.

AtomServiceDocument

Supports the discovery of the capabilities and locations of available AtomWorkspace organized using one or more AtomWorkspace.

AtomWorkspace

Represents a server-defined group of AtomMemberResources objects that describe member resources.
